name: 德鲁·肯尼
introduction: Actor, producer, and model Drew Kenney was born in Phoenix, Arizona and is based in Los Angeles, California. Drew has appeared in such shows as Veronica Mars, Special, American Horror Story, The Bold And The Beautiful, The Catch, Adam Ruins Everything, The Ellen Show, and The Bachelorette. Drew's film credits include Two Ways To Go West, Ulysses; A Dark Oddysey, Blood Trap, and Famous Adjacent. Drew has performed in stage productions of On An Average Day and Be True To Thy Selfie. Drew continues his training in Los Angeles at the Nancy Banks Studio and is a graduate from The Second City Hollywood.
